WEBVTT

00:08:59.576 --> 00:09:00.807
than it is for them.

00:09:00.831 --> 00:09:02.593
And I'd also like to ask you a favor.

00:09:02.617 --> 00:09:05.576
If you're ever successful
in arranging one of these visits,

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:06.918
please tell me about it.

00:09:08.064 --> 00:09:09.760
The other part of my family's story

00:09:09.784 --> 00:09:12.096
is that we ended up visiting
all four facilities

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:14.182
that received Thomas's donations.

00:09:14.206 --> 00:09:17.130
And we met amazing people
doing inspiring work.

00:09:18.003 --> 00:09:23.104
The way I see it now
is that Thomas got into Harvard,

00:09:23.128 --> 00:09:25.294
Duke and Penn --

00:09:25.318 --> 00:09:28.643
(Laughter)

00:09:28.667 --> 00:09:31.035
And he has a job at Cytonet,